select shop_id,
       receiving_scan_time,

       case when status = 0 then 'off' when status = 1 then 'on' end as status,
       receiving_scan_flag,
       user_id,
       mobile,
       address,
       vid,
       vcid,
       tcid,
       item_num,
       purchase_price,
       total_amount,
       tid,
       is_lack,
       city_market_id,
       is_same_city,
       product_label_status,
       qc_status,
       create_time,
       pay_time,
       dt
from dwd_old_order_df_test
where receiving_scan_time >= '2022-10-01';
